  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK486">
<l>ūkka muṭaiyā ṉoṭukkam porutakar</l>
<l>tākkaṟkup pērun takaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The self-restraint of the energetic (while waiting for a suitable opportunity), is like the drawing back of a fighting-ram in order to butt.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
